<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="89" type="description">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="89">Description.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="89">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">
Male. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">Head</emphasis>
</emphasis>
(Fig. 
<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 5" captionStartId="F5" captionText="Figure 5. Heteroconis yunnanensis sp. nov., holotype male a habitus, lateral view b head, dorsal view c forewing d hindwing. Scale bar: 1 mm." figureDoi="10.3897/zookeys.1081.72606.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/632929" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">5a, b</figureCitation>
). Fuscous. Frons with a pair of lateral knobs above antennae and a median projection between antennae. Eyes dark. Antennae 18-segmented. Basal eight and apical two flagellomeres whitish, the others dark brown. Both third and fourth flagellomeres with a short spine. Scape about 3-times as long as broad. Pedicel 2-times as long as broad. Four basal segments of maxillary palp dark brown, apical palpomere whitish. Labial palps dark brown.
</paragraph>
<caption doi="10.3897/zookeys.1081.72606.figure5" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/632929" pageId="0" pageNumber="89" start="Figure 5" startId="F5">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="89">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">Figure 5.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Zhao &amp; Sziráki &amp; Liu" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Coniopterygidae" genus="Heteroconis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Heteroconis yunnanensis" order="Neuroptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="89" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="yunnanensis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">Heteroconis yunnanensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sp. nov., holotype male 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">a</emphasis>
habitus, lateral view 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">b</emphasis>
head, dorsal view 
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="89">c</emphasis>
